org.apache.drill.exec.physical.resultSet.project

Class TestProjectedTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest
      • org.apache.drill.exec.physical.resultSet.project.TestProjectedTuple

  • public class TestProjectedTuple
extends BaseTest
    Test the projection list parser: parses a list of SchemaPath items into a detailed structure, handling duplicate or overlapping items. Special cases the select-all (SELECT *) and select none (SELECT COUNT(*)) cases.

    These tests should verify everything about (runtime) projection parsing; the only bits not tested here is that which is inherently specific to some use case.
